text: Kudakwashe Munyede (born 30 April 1991) is a Zimbabwean first-class cricketer who plays for Mid West Rhinos. He made his Twenty20 debut for Zimbabwe against Eastern Province in the 2016 Africa T20 Cup on 30 September 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Mashonaland Eagles cricketers Category:Mid West Rhinos cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Harare
